  <article class="container" id="challenge-research">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="text-center">
          <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/shingo/image/upload/c_scale,w_300/v1478283005/WebDesign/Logos/Research-Award-Logo.png" alt="Research Award Logo" />
        </div>
        <div class="nine centered text-center columns">
            <h2 class="quattrocento">Shingo Research Award</h2>
            <h4>This award recognizes and promotes research and writing that has had a significant impact and advances the body of knowledge regarding operational excellence. The Shingo Institute is most interested in recognizing thought leadership.</h4>
        </div>
    </div>
    <br>
    <div class="row">
  		<h4><strong>Award Criteria</strong></h4>
      <h6>Submissions are assessed based on the following criteria:</h6>
  		<ul class="square">
  			<li>Content – contributes new operational excellence knowledge, or significantly extends and supports existing operational excellence knowledge</li>
  			<li>Significant Impact – documented by the number and quality of citations in scholarly literature (excluding self-citation), reviews in specific relevant journals, or business performance improvements. The submission’s actual impact is an important element of the assessment criteria; therefore, research may not be eligible if appropriate documentation of impact is not provided.</li>
  			<li>Premise</li>
  			<li>Presentation</li>
        <li>Approach</li>
  		</ul>
  		<h6>Types of accepted submission include:</h6>
  		<ul class="square">
  			<li>Books</li>
  			<li>Articles</li>
  			<li>Case studies</li>
  		</ul>

  		<p><strong>All works must be published at the time of submission. Applications are accepted continuously throughout the year.</strong></p>
      <div class="row text-center">
        <div class="medium secondary rounded btn"><a href="assets/Research-Award-Application-Form.pdf" target="_blank">Research Award Application</a></div>
      </div>
      <br>
      <div class="twelve columns">
          <table class="striped">
            <tbody>
            	<tr>
                <td colspan="3"><h4 class="roboto"><strong>Research Award Recipients</strong></h4></td>
              </tr>
              {{#each awards}}
      		    <tr>
                <td>{{prettyMonth Press_Release_Date__c}}</td>
                <td><a href="/researchaward/{{Id}}">{{Name}}</td>
                <td>{{Public_Author_Name__c}}</td>
              </tr>
              {{/each}}
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
